Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.89,0:00:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mighty Little Defenders 2: The Intriguing Alien Guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:16.77,Title,,0,0,0,,The Search for the Sun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.98,end,,0,0,0,,End
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s still no sign of BB Goat ’s brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.40,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s going to feel let down again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fulfill some of BB Goat ’s wishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she’d be very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.84,0:00:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all sorts of different candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can read her all sorts of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help her make all sorts of beautiful clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take her wherever she wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.68,0:01:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ’s just a little girl, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sure her wishes will be very easy to fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find Mr. Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what Mr. Sun does after sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that’s a bit easier to fulfill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you say that any wish would be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sun’s almost setting, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How exactly are we supposed to search?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Searching for the Sun, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t you knock first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat  is looking for the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can transform into a sun and get close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I’ll jump in and capture her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sun is round…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s round…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did my soccer ball go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here’s my Super Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sun glows…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It glows…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I put the light bulbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I can switch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very strange bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must you always disturb me when I’m in focus mode?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can already glow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so all you need now is to transform into a Sun-shaped light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat  won’t be able to meet him anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so let’s just make up a story about what the Sun does
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,after sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After sunset, the Sun transforms into the light on an anglerfish’s head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,illuminating the oceans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the anglerfish exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Sun over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The fish ate Mr. Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the anglerfish’s own little bulbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,not Mr. Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what {\i1}does{\i0} Mr. Sun do after sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After sunset, he becomes Santa Claus,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,going out every now and then to send presents to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun sends presents, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Santa Claus meet-and-greet is happening tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t miss it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Santa Claus’ identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve run out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,let’s search for Mr. Sun underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Sun really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun has had a long day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and he’s out of power now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After sunset, he has to stay in a cave to recharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, what exactly have you planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I buried a toy sun in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just have her follow the map I made, and she’ll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I found Mr. Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The toy sun is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what did BB Goat  dig up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we won’t find Mr. Sun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.29,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be sure to help you find Mr. Sun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Brother Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s head up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:06:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,have you thought of an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,what exactly is your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll buy some time with BB Goat 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and have someone appear all dressed up as the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,since you can control heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you can use a flashlight to add some glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re best suited for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ’s right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In a moment, transform into the Sun and lure her over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Brother Sparky go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,—He’s going to the bathroom.　—He forgot to water the plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,—He forgot to water the plants.　—He’s going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat ,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take you to pick some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.41,0:08:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll join you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,we’ll just wait for Sparky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to finish dressing up as the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat , Mr. Sun is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a realistic Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How are they not suspicious of Goldy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, why did they mention Sparky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,where’s BB Goat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,BB Goat  and the others went to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They’ll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How does he know what I’m thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re Sparky?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where did this Sun come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it. I think it’s over for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want BB Goat  to undo the seal, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,SInce she’s not here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll deal with you guys first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack them now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was blinding. I can’t see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you bring sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to cover my third eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest that you hand over BB Goat 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and save yourselves the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way we’re doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s split up and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we attack together, we’ll be blinded by the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No more chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.41,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he sneak up on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Flash him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I’m made of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s your chance to attack, Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It won’t matter how many times you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you take the sunglasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was thanks to Paddi pulling the sunglasses over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s Mr. Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Sun sleeps in the forest after sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, guys? Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sun is tired from providing light all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s let him sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and not disturb him.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
